name: Flag of Portugal
description:
Portugal is a country in Southwestern Europe.

In this edition of r/place, Portugal had sole presence and organisation of members of the Portuguese Reddit community without the logistical help of r/Portugal due to the API restrictions that were made effective in 2023.

By the initiative of some members of the Portuguese Community and by the acceptance of some famous portuguese streamers like SirKazzio and Wuant, the portuguese had a successful participation in this year's r/Place.
